# The Dell installer .deb is re-downloadable from dl.dell.com — see
# Dell_U4025QW_FirmwareUpdate_Instruction_Ubuntu_A00.pdf inside the
# .deb (or PLUGIN_NOTES.md) for the URL pattern. Not committed to keep
# the repo small (and history-rewritten out of older commits 2026-05).
U4025QW_M3T105.deb
*.deb

# Wire-protocol pcaps are large (≥10 MB) and contain the same payloads
# the decompiled C and PLUGIN_NOTES.md reference — re-record with
# Wireshark + USBcapture if you need to replay. History-rewritten out
# of older commits 2026-05 (the main update pcap also exceeds GitHub's
# 100 MB hard limit).
captures/*.pcapng
captures/*.pcap

# Reconstructible from U4025QW_M3T105.deb via dpkg -x / -e
extracted/
extracted-control/

# Probe artefacts
page.html

# Cross-monitor key-comparison .deb files (re-downloadable from dl.dell.com;
# see comparison/<model>/README.md for URLs). Extracted plugin .so's would
# be the only useful artifacts and they're easy to regenerate.
comparison/*/*.deb
comparison/*/extracted/

# Decryption derivable from `ecies-decrypt` + the captured input blob.
captures/decrypted-*.bin
